OL,3,CHarry marks Invictus Games countdown
OL,4,Cwith pickleball and rugby - but no
OL,5,CMeghan
OL,7,FPrince Harry has shown off his racquet
OL,8,Fskills at an event to mark one year
OL,9,Fcountdown to the Invictus Games.
OL,11,FThe Duke of Sussex tried tennis-
OL,12,Falternative pickleball, which will
OL,13,Fdebut at next year's games, during a
OL,14,Fceremony in Birmingham's NEC on
OL,15,FFriday. He also participated in a
OL,16,Fwheelchair rugby session.
OL,18,FThe venue will host the tournament for
OL,19,Fwounded, injured and sick military
OL,20,Fveterans in July 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
