OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783703991
OL,3,CHarry marks Invictus Games countdown
OL,4,Cwith pickleball and rugby - but no
OL,5,CMeghan
OL,7,FMeghan Markle had been due to attend
OL,8,Fthe event, but delayed her trip to the
OL,9,FUK because of security concerns.
OL,11,FBut the duchess is widely expected to
OL,12,Fbe travelling to the UK with their
OL,13,Fchildren, Prince Archie and Princess
OL,14,FLilibet.
OL,16,FITV News understands that last-minute
OL,17,Fdiscussions have been taking place
OL,18,Fover the past few days regarding a
OL,19,Fmeeting between Prince Harry and his
OL,20,Ffather, King Charles.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
