PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1783703991
OL,3,CHarry marks Invictus Games countdown
OL,4,Cwith pickleball and rugby - but no
OL,5,CMeghan
OL,7,FThey are trying to find a mutually
OL,8,Fconvenient time and location for the
OL,9,Ffather and son to see each other, but
OL,10,Fstaff in both camps are suspicious of
OL,11,Fthe others' motives, Royal Editor
OL,12,FChris Ship wrote.
OL,14,FThe latest arrangements centre on
OL,15,FHarry travelling to meet the King at
OL,16,Fhis Highgrove estate in
OL,17,FGloucestershire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
