OL,3,CHarry marks Invictus Games countdown
OL,4,Cwith pickleball and rugby - but no
OL,5,CMeghan
OL,7,FHelen Helliwell, chief executive
OL,8,Fofficer of Invictus Games Birmingham
OL,9,F2027, opened the event with the words:
OL,10,F"Invictus has always been more than a
OL,11,Fweek of games."
OL,13,FShe added: "It transforms lives not
OL,14,Fonly for competitors but for their
OL,15,Ffamilies."
