OL,3,CHarry marks Invictus Games countdown
OL,4,Cwith pickleball and rugby - but no
OL,5,CMeghan
OL,7,FHarry was joined by This Morning and
OL,8,FGreat British Bake Off host Alison
OL,9,FHammond, who is from Birmingham, and
OL,10,FTV presenter Ade Adepitan, who won a
OL,11,Fbronze with the GB basketball team at
OL,12,Fthe 2004 Paralympics.
OL,14,FThe duke joined a partner on court to
OL,15,Fcompete against another pair in
OL,16,Fpickleball, which will make an
OL,17,Fappearance when the games are staged
OL,18,Fin Birmingham next year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
